author: Brett Worthington
title: Bipartisan push for inquiry into China's handling of the coronavirus outbreak
description: Labor backs Marise Payne's call for a global inquiry to be held into the origins of the coronavirus pandemic, with the Foreign Minister calling for the probe to be run independently of the World Health Organisation.
content:
Updated 
April 19, 2020 17:04:26
A bipartisan push has begun for a global inquiry into the origins of the coronavirus pandemic, including China's handling of the initial outbreak in the city of Wuhan.
